version.description: The version of the Mini Program you want to jump to, valid values are develop, trial, and release, and the online version must be set to release
version.description_zh: 跳转到的小程序版本，有效值 develop（开发版），trial（体验版），release（正式版）；线上版本必须设置为 release

name.description: The feature page to jump to

args.description: Parameters and format of function pages are related to specific function pages
args.description_zh: 功能页参数，参数格式与具体功能页相关

onSuccess.description: The function page is returned, and it is triggered when the operation is successful, and the detail format is related to the specific function page
onSuccess.description_zh: 功能页返回，且操作成功时触发， detail 格式与具体功能页相关

onFail.description: The function page is returned, and it is triggered when the operation fails, and the detail format is related to the specific function page
onFail.description_zh: 功能页返回，且操作失败时触发， detail 格式与具体功能页相关

onCancel.description: Triggered when a user action returns from a function page
onCancel.description_zh: 因用户操作从功能页返回时触发
